vote.title: An ordinance abandoning portions of a utility easement, wastewater easement and avigation easement to OH Maplewood, LP, the abutting owner, containing a total of approximately 45,026 square feet of land, located near the intersection of Denton Drive and Denton Drive Cut-Off; and providing for the dedication of a total of approximately 9,925 square feet of land needed for sidewalk easements - Revenue: General Fund $5,400.00, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
